properties.Name: FocusGroup
properties.Description:
A special interest group that focuses upon a specific Product or Product usage.

Focus Groups are most often manufacturer-sponsored groups designed to provide feedback directly to the manufacturer regarding their products prior to product mass marketing.

Columns.Name: FocusGroupId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of the Focus Group.

Columns.Name: FocusGroupName
Columns.Description: The name of the Focus Group.

Columns.Name: FocusGroupDescription
Columns.Description: The description of the Focus Group.
